		  <div class="panel-body">
			<p>PAD Rater was designed and created by a Puzzle and Dragons fan just like the rest of you.</p>
			<p>Just like how the PAD community has helped me so much, I would like to provide something in return.</p>
			<p>Web development is a side hobby of mine. I am an L2 support analyst full time.
			PAD Rater started as a side project, trying to make better use of my free time at work.</p>
			<p>PAD Rater is intended to be North America's community driven game8 with additional features.
			There are many posts on reddit asking what is the optimal team to use a specific leader especially after god fests.
			This site was created with the intention to address those questions.</p>
			<p>With a full time job, keeping content up to date is a difficult task. This is where the community comes in.
			Not only one or two individuals, but the entire community can make this all happen.</p>
